OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNo uniform choice for      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FVirgin crew on World Cup   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fflight                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Virgin Atlantic has said its           
OL,6, gender-neutral uniform policy does not 
OL,7, apply to the crew on board the England 
OL,8, team's flight to the World Cup in      
OL,9, Qatar.                                 
OL,11,FThe airline announced a "fluid         
OL,12,Fapproach" to uniforms in September that
OL,13,Fit said allowed staff to choose their  
OL,14,Fattire "no matter their gender".       
OL,16,FBut a spokeswoman told BBC News the    
OL,17,Fcrew for Tuesday's flight to Doha would
OL,18,Fnot be able to choose their uniform.   
OL,20,FVirgin said a plane displaying an LGBT 
OL,21,Ficon would be used for the journey.    
